  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of ATG003 in Patients With AMD Receiving Anti-VEGF</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2 Randomized, Double-Masked, Study to Evaluate the Safety and Preliminary Efficacy of ATG003 in Patients With Neovascular Age-Related Macular Degeneration (NV-AMD) Receiving Frequent Maintenance Intravitreal Anti-VEGF Antibody Therapy (Ranibizumab or Bevacizumab)</official_title>
